{"tid":996794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵車廂聽到咁樣既對話","createTime":"2019-01-26T14:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T15:14:29.000Z","uid":209242,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"89b6ac1fb3e305b65a5aed9247530539ce6c56b7","tid":996794,"uid":209242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"返工返到隻狗咁攰<br />\n上咗地鐵返屋企<br />\n<br />\n見到一個家庭好溫馨<br />\n兩老+爸爸媽媽+哥哥妹妹<br />\n<br />\n哥哥妹妹年齡約十歲與五歲左右<br />\n<br />\n公公比咗封利是哥哥<br />\n哥哥袋好之後<br />\n媽媽隨口就問：<br />\n啊！之前啊姨封利是比啊妹你幫佢擺起咗喺邊到？<br />\n<br />\n哥哥猶豫咗一陣答：唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n妹妹順口就話喇：<br />\n封利是得五十蚊咋嘛，跌咗都唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我記得我仲係5歲嗰陣...<br />\n廿蚊利是已經好開心<br />\n可以買下零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5061c38dd38b0af2e8931a6448a8cc66ce50c92c","tid":996794,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"擺明阿哥食咗"},{"pid":"dbf0e705f9cc87648bc5b02f8457701f7c144476","tid":996794,"uid":54162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"可能妹妹唔想呀哥唔開心 先扮唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dd56a26d02e5e53f4698c76845df6cdadc8140","tid":996794,"uid":209242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5061c38dd38b0af2e8931a6448a8cc66ce50c92c","tid":996794,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"擺明阿哥食咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:54:31.000Z","msg":"啊哥仲要係肥底 一定去咗買好多薯片JapJapJap"},{"pid":"6a890b1b479a0a828a6334de1a0aa8494ed6bd8c","tid":996794,"uid":209242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbf0e705f9cc87648bc5b02f8457701f7c144476","tid":996794,"uid":54162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime